mapkurator-spotter-mps
=======================

This project is an Apple Silicon (MPS/CPU) port of the mapKurator "spotter-v2"
text spotter. It contains original packaging (a Nix flake and CLI wrapper) plus
a small source patch; it does NOT vendor or redistribute the upstream code or
model weights — those are fetched from their original locations at build/run
time.

Upstream source
---------------
mapkurator-spotter (spotter-v2)
