  - TESTR (Deformable-DETR text spotter)

Model weights
-------------
The spotter checkpoints (e.g. model_v2_en.pth) are published by the upstream
authors on Google Drive and are governed by the upstream license and the
per-model model cards. They are NOT included here. Use scripts/get-weights.sh to
download them for non-commercial use.

What this repository adds
-------------------------
  - patches/apple-mps.patch — routes multi-scale deformable attention through
    the pure-PyTorch reference (no compiled CUDA op) and replaces the legacy
    Tensor.type(<string>) API with .to(dtype) so the model runs on the MPS
    backend. This is the port.
  - flake.nix — reproducible Nix packaging and a `mapkurator-spotter` CLI.
  - scripts/ — weight download and a developer checkout helper.
